# AUTHORS — llm-baremetal

This file records the main attribution for the public baremetal repository.
Git history remains the authoritative record of authorship and contribution.

## Original author

Djiby Diop (@Djiby-diop)

## Public baremetal contribution areas

- UEFI boot and firmware runtime
- bare-metal inference pipeline
- memory management and low-level support code
- build, test, and release scripts

## Third-party components used in this repository

- llama2.c by Andrej Karpathy (MIT)
- gnu-efi (BSD)
- ARM optimized-routines (MIT)
- bestline by Justine Tunney (ISC)
- jtckdint by Justine Tunney (ISC)
- GGUF / GGML-derived k-quant dequantisation math (MIT / Apache-2.0)

